Package: RForInvt
Type: Package
Title: Forest Inventory Data Compilation and FVS Growth Projections
Version: 0.3.0
Author: Jacob Strunk
Maintainer: Jacob Strunk <someone@somewhere.com>
Description: A collection of data processing tools and helpers motivated by
        forest inventory analysis, and a companion to RSForTools (Remote Sensing
        Forestry Tools). It provides utilities for compiling tree- and
        plot-level inventory summaries, running Forest Vegetation Simulator
        (FVS) growth projections, wrapping the National Volume Estimator Library
        (NVEL) for volume, bucking, merchandizing and biomass, archiving and
        applying fitted models, and design-based estimation. The functionality
        is developmental and provided without warranty; contributions are
        welcome.
License: GPL (>= 2)
